#### Edit 2 — Detection check (insert after line 1644, before the GPT-OSS block)

```cpp
    // Mistral Instruct v0.3 - [INST]/[/INST] user delimiters, system prepended
    // to first user turn.  Absence of [SYSTEM_PROMPT] distinguishes it from
    // Ministral 3 / Devstral which wrap the system block separately.
    if (src.find("[INST]") != std::string::npos &&
        src.find("[SYSTEM_PROMPT]") == std::string::npos) {
        LOG_DBG("Using specialized template: Mistral Instruct v0.3\n");
        return common_chat_params_init_mistral_instruct_v3(tmpl, params);
    }
```

